# Mindspace About Page - Shattered Voronoi Glass Design

A comprehensive redesign of the `/about` page featuring interactive shattered Voronoi glass effects with the sky background image, incorporating laser zoom interactions and a cosmic-map-style side panel.

---

## Design Overview

Based on the provided references, this page will create an **immersive mindspace experience** that feels like looking through shattered glass fragments, each containing "about me" topics/concepts. The sky background ([/bg.png](file:///c:/Users/giant/Documents/GitHub/thuh.cool/public/bg.png)) will show through each glass fragment with glassmorphism effects.

### Core Visual Elements

| Element | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Voronoi Tessellation** | Dynamic shattered glass pattern using D3.js Delaunay triangulation |
| **Glassmorphism Fragments** | Each shard shows the sky image with blur and transparency effects |
| **Nodes/Labels** | Personal "about me" topics placed at cell centers |
| **Interactive Zoom** | Laser-like smooth zoom when clicking nodes |
| **Side Panel** | Cosmic-map style sliding panel with node details |

### Key Interactions

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[Hover Fragment] --> B[Glass Highlight]
    B --> C[Topic Label Reveals]
    C --> D[Click Node]
    D --> E[Laser Zoom Effect]
    E --> F[Side Panel Slides In]
    F --> G[Click Outside/X]
    G --> H[Smooth Zoom Out]
```

