## Technical Implementation Details

### Voronoi Glass Effect with Sky Background

```tsx
// Each cell will have a clipPath and show the background
<svg>
  <defs>
    <clipPath id="cell-0">
      <path d={cell.path} />
    </clipPath>
  </defs>
  <g clipPath="url(#cell-0)">
    <image href="/bg.png" x="0" y="0" width="100%" height="100%"
           style={{ filter: 'blur(1px)' }} />
    <rect fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)" />
  </g>
</svg>
```

### Laser Zoom Transform

```tsx
// Following cosmic_map_reference.tsx pattern
const transformStyle = useMemo(() => {
  if (selectedIndex !== null) {
    const target = nodes[selectedIndex];
    // Center viewport on target, scale up
    return {
      transform: `translate(${cx}px, ${cy}px) scale(3) translate(${-target.x}px, ${-target.y}px)`,
      transition: 'transform 1.5s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1)'
    };
  }
  return {
    transform: 'translate(0, 0) scale(1)',
    transition: 'transform 1.5s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1)'
  };
}, [selectedIndex, nodes]);
```

